snippet.textDisplay:
literally what.. I'm not even present in the space and I am sooo overwhelmed with emotions and feels, I'm so proud of Jeffree and everything he's accomplished within the past 6 years and to have been on this journey with him for the last 2 years makes me realize truly anything is possible if you work hard and trust in yourself. Damn Jeffree you just changed my perspective on life, I'm only 16 years old and I have a few things going for me - art being the main one but also any other creative subject but you made me realize if I work my ass off now in school and in art doing commissions and such- I can live easy in the future with bigger and more rewarding opportunities. This whole time I feel like I've just been existing but you smacked that thought of hope and believing in yourself into me so hard that I have the immense sense of ' i need to get this shit over and done with and work on my own projects. I need to study and teach myself what's important and thrive'. As a token of love and appreciation for everything you've taught me Jeffree, one day once I have the money, materials and time I hope to create an art piece that you will treasure and keep close to your heart. I don't want your money for it I simply want you to know you're admired and have played an important role in my life. for gods sake Jeffree thank you just thank you! I wish all the best for you and your future projects.
I may be nothing now, but see me in a few years. we shall be in contact about that art piece ;)
<3
(just as proof of me being a hopeful artist : @smach3002 is my insta, don't mean to self promote but I'll also be open to commissions in the next month or so .. hit me up if you want one >;D) ALSO HAPPY NEW YEAR THE FUCK
